{"tid":1491894,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"824 觀塘路標(燈塔) 遊客搵路","createTime":"2019-08-20T15:05:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T15:05:52.000Z","uid":234178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a02fe61a57c9941d5996e0c3627892733fcc7edb","tid":1491894,"uid":234178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:05:52.000Z","msg":"利申: 第一次開po<br />\n<br />\n無論揀去機場定觀塘 目標清晰就可以事半功倍<br />\n觀塘咁多去處 好容易走失<br />\n為咗大家唔好蕩失路 從政府公開資料中整合咗啲路標 方便遊客搵路<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>[整合] 燈燈燈地圖</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mapcustomizer.com/map/%E7%87%88%E7%87%88%E7%87%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mapcustomizer.com%2Fmap%2F%25E7%2587%2588%25E7%2587%2588%25E7%2587%2588&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9mCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=aa56a66d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mapcustomizer.com/map/%E7%87%88%E7%87%88%E7%87%88</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">資料來源:<br />\n燈柱數據: <a href=\"https://data.gov.hk/tc-data/dataset/hk-landsd-openmap-geodetic-smartlp-positioning\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdata.gov.hk%2Ftc-data%2Fdataset%2Fhk-landsd-openmap-geodetic-smartlp-positioning&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9mCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=59c41779\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://data.gov.hk/tc-data/dataset/hk-landsd-openmap-geodetic-smartlp-positioning</a><br />\n數據字典: <a href=\"https://www.geodetic.gov.hk/common/data/LP/DataDict_LP.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.geodetic.gov.hk%2Fcommon%2Fdata%2FLP%2FDataDict_LP.pdf&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9mCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=0ce13342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.geodetic.gov.hk/common/data/LP/DataDict_LP.pdf</a><br />\n地理資訊地圖: <a href=\"https://www.map.gov.hk/gm/map/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.map.gov.hk%2Fgm%2Fmap%2F&d=TRt9Hu9y5T%2Bqj71zgJeH9mCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=07bcc113\